</div></nav></div></header></div><main role="main" id="contenu"><div class="drupal-parme bg-drupal-primary"><div class="mx-auto max-w-[73rem] px-5 pt-[6.25rem] pb-12 lg:flex lg:items-center lg:justify-between lg:px-10 lg:pt-[12.5rem]"><div class="ecoMode:relative ecoMode:pb-[480px] ecoMode:md:pb-0 w-full lg:pr-[7.5rem]"><div class="hidden ecoMode:block" aria-hidden="false"><div class="bg-repeat-space bg-eco-mode-cobalt absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 scale-[0.85] md:static md:translate-x-0" style="background-image:url(&#x27;/images/svg/mode-eco/motrice.svg&#x27;);background-size:20px 20px;width:467px;height:480px;mask-image:url(&#x27;/images/svg/mode-eco/event-header.svg&#x27;)"></div></div><div class="ecoMode:hidden" aria-hidden="false"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="467" height="480" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="mt-9 mb-[3.88rem]" style="color:transparent" src="https://www.groupe-sncf.com/medias-publics/styles/crop_1_1/public/2025-09/header-Coulisses.png.webp?VersionId=6qeAgBmgxZ4N4btnRy_1vDXDHAPGd5vD&amp;itok=Fe7sk8H9"/></div></div><div class="text-drupal-secondary w-full"><h2 class="rgaa-leading-up mb-2 text-[2rem] leading-[2.625rem] font-bold lg:mb-8 lg:text-[3.125rem] lg:leading-[3.625rem]">Suivez-nous en coulisses</h2><div class="rgaa-leading-up mb-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.625rem] font-light lg:mb-8 lg:text-[1.375rem] lg:leading-[1.875rem]"><p>Découvrez, à travers nos vidéos courtes et diaporamas, des projets que vous ne soupçonnez pas et qui pourtant changent la donne.</p></div><a class="btn btn-primary max-md:btn-full-center" href="/fr/coulisses">Par ici la visite !</a></div></div></div><div class="container mx-auto max-w-[1120px] px-5 md:px-0 md:mb-[6rem] mt-12 mb-[72px] lg:mb-12 lg:mt-[72px]"><h2 class="mb-8 whitespace-break-spaces text-balance text-[32px] font-bold leading-[42px] md:mb-5 md:text-50px md:leading-[58px]">Découvrez notre actualité</h2><div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-8 md:flex-row md:items-end"></div></div><div class="container mx-auto max-w-[1120px] px-5 md:px-0 md:mb-[6rem] mt-12 mb-[72px] lg:mb-24 lg:mt-[72px]"><div class="swiper"><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide group !h-auto"><div class="drupal-bleu-horizon rounded-10px text-true-black bg-drupal-primary flex h-full shrink-0 flex-grow flex-col cursor-pointer higherLineHeight:min-h-[560px] min-h-[510px] w-[264px] higherLineHeight:md:!min-h-[720px] fontDyslexic:md:min-h-[660px] md:min-h-[640px] md:w-[400px] ecoMode:border ecoMode:border-cobalt/20" data-index="0"><div></div><div class="rounded-b-10px flex flex-1 flex-col dark:text-blanc p-6 md:p-8 ecoMode:border-opacity-0"><h3 class="drupal-bleu-horizon font-bold [&amp;_span]:bg-blanc dark:[&amp;_span]:bg-true-black [&amp;_span]:px-1 [&amp;_span]:text-inherit text-22px higherLineHeight:leading-10 leading-8 text-drupal-secondary dark:text-drupal-secondary md:text-40px md:leading-[60px] higherLineHeight:md:leading-[64px] fontDyslexic:md:text-32px"><p>Lasers, capteurs et radars ultra-performants pour <span>surveiller le réseau</span></p></h3><div class="flex flex-grow flex-col"><div class="flex flex-grow items-start pt-6 text-pretty md:items-center md:pt-0"><div><p>Nous innovons dans l’inspection de nos voies et caténaires afin de toujours mieux protéger l’infrastructure.</p></div></div><span class="min-h-[21px]"><a class="font-bold cursor-pointer rounded-sm outline-offset-8 text-cobalt dark:text-bleu-horizon outline-dark-cobalt dark:outline-light-cobalt break-all" data-prefetch="false" tabindex="-1" href="/fr/innovation/technologies-emergentes/surveillance-reseau"><span class="border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-inherit">En savoir plus<i aria-hidden="true" aria-label="hidden" class="icon icon-chevron-right text-[0.7em] pl-2 translate-y-px __variable_bc4094"></i></span></a></span></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide group !h-auto"><div class="drupal-vert-eau rounded-10px text-true-black bg-drupal-primary flex h-full shrink-0 flex-grow flex-col cursor-pointer higherLineHeight:min-h-[560px] min-h-[510px] w-[264px] higherLineHeight:md:!min-h-[720px] fontDyslexic:md:min-h-[660px] md:min-h-[640px] md:w-[400px] ecoMode:border ecoMode:border-cobalt/20" data-index="1"><div></div><div class="rounded-b-10px flex flex-1 flex-col dark:text-blanc p-6 md:p-8 ecoMode:border-opacity-0"><h3 class="drupal-vert-eau font-bold [&amp;_span]:bg-blanc dark:[&amp;_span]:bg-true-black [&amp;_span]:px-1 [&amp;_span]:text-inherit text-22px higherLineHeight:leading-10 leading-8 text-drupal-secondary dark:text-drupal-secondary md:text-40px md:leading-[60px] higherLineHeight:md:leading-[64px] fontDyslexic:md:text-32px"><p>En <span>Inde</span>, bientôt un <span>métro</span> exclusivement conduit par des <span>femmes</span></p></h3><div class="flex flex-grow flex-col"><div class="flex flex-grow items-start pt-6 text-pretty md:items-center md:pt-0"><div><p>Keolis a été choisi pour exploiter la future ligne 3 du métro de Pune. 100 femmes seront prochainement recrutées et formées par notre société pour conduire les rames du métro de cette ville de 8 millions d’habitants.</p></div></div><span class="min-h-[21px]"><a class="font-bold cursor-pointer rounded-sm outline-offset-8 text-cobalt dark:text-bleu-horizon outline-dark-cobalt dark:outline-light-cobalt break-all" data-prefetch="false" tabindex="-1" href="/fr/groupe/portrait-entreprise/groupe-societes/keolis/exploitation-metro-pune-inde"><span class="border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-inherit">En savoir plus<i aria-hidden="true" aria-label="hidden" class="icon icon-chevron-right text-[0.7em] pl-2 translate-y-px __variable_bc4094"></i></span></a></span></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide group !h-auto"><div class="drupal-transparent rounded-10px text-true-black bg-drupal-primary flex h-full shrink-0 flex-grow flex-col cursor-pointer higherLineHeight:min-h-[560px] min-h-[510px] w-[264px] higherLineHeight:md:!min-h-[720px] fontDyslexic:md:min-h-[660px] md:min-h-