rsor-pointer hover:shadow-md overflow-hidden transition-all ease-in-out hover:scale-105 flex flex-col items-center justify-around py-14 md:py-10 drupal-parme bg-drupal-secondary text-drupal-primary md:justify-between"><div class="absolute -top-20 -right-36 md:-top-8 md:-right-16 md:hidden"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="356" height="168" viewBox="0 0 356 168" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19.9949 2.86328C19.6695 3.47618 19.4095 4.23233 19.2233 5.16598C19.2233 5.16598 0.716955 116.271 0.396409 118.284C-0.274527 122.493 0.813095 124.4 4.5074 126.118C121.855 181.019 284.049 168.593 357.061 158.331C367.531 156.86 376.161 155.434 382.567 154.258C385.175 153.778 387.113 152.679 388.056 150.899C388.623 149.826 388.829 148.507 388.606 146.925L362.194 -41.0077C361.732 -44.2962 358.996 -46.9355 355.436 -46.4351L25.3457 -0.0368905C23.0404 0.287092 21.1246 0.726473 19.9949 2.86328Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div><div class="ecoMode:hidden" aria-hidden="false"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="200" height="200" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-10px hidden w-full md:block" style="color:transparent" src="https://www.groupe-sncf.com/medias-publics/2025-09/parapluie.svg?VersionId=zJw0Vy5oMEbrqIkOwlDTyxu2Cj_UYL2g"/></div><div class="mt-20 h-[180px] max-w-[280px] text-center flex flex-col justify-center md:h-initial md:mt-0"><h3 class="higherLineHeight:leading-[2rem] md:text-22px mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Jupiter</h3><div class="wysiwyg text-pretty"></div><button class="sr-only" type="button" aria-label="Choisir la réponse Jupiter">Choisir la réponse Jupiter</button></div></div><div data-testid="quiz-answer-2-reveal" style="box-shadow:0px 4px 80px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.10)" class="absolute w-full h-full px-6 rounded-10px cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md overflow-hidden transition-all ease-in-out hover:scale-105 bg-blanc dark:bg-[#42505A] text-center rotate-y-180 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 hidden"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="144" height="144" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="hidden md:block" style="color:transparent" src="/images/character.svg"/><h4 class="z-20 text-xl font-bold dark:text-blanc">Eh non, pas cette fois-ci.</h4><div class="dark:text-blanc wysiwyg text-pretty"><p class="">C’est l’équivalent de Zeus chez les Romains.</p></div><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Rejouez</button></div></div></li></ul></div><div class="drupal-vert-eau bg-drupal-primary text-drupal-secondary h-full w-full pt-8 md:pt-16"><div class="container mx-auto max-w-[1120px] px-5 md:px-0 py-5 ecoMode:md:mb-0 md:mb-[3rem]"><h2 class="rgaa-leading-up mb-2 max-w-full text-[2rem] leading-[2.625rem] font-bold md:max-w-[738px] lg:mb-8 lg:text-[3.125rem] lg:leading-[3.625rem]">Un champion français de taille mondiale</h2><div class="ecoMode:md:mb-24 flex flex-col justify-between gap-8 md:flex-row md:items-end"><div class="higherLineHeight:leading-42px md:text-22px text-lg md:w-[738px] wysiwyg text-pretty"><p class="">Avec 290 000 collaborateurs dont 73 000 hors de France, notre Groupe réalise un tiers de son activité à l&#x27;international. Elle s&#x27;articule autour de trois principaux marchés : la logistique de marchandises dans un réseau de 170 pays, le mass transit sur les 5 continents et le transport de voyageurs à grande vitesse.</p></div><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/fr/groupe/international">Découvrez nos activités à l&#x27;international</a></div></div><div class="ecoMode:hidden" aria-hidden="false"><a href="/fr/groupe/international"><picture><source srcSet="https://www.groupe-sncf.com/medias-publics/styles/original/public/2024-09/groupe-sncf-international-mobile-fond-transparent-l.png.webp?VersionId=mBXLrgzPC4AQmsn9Bvd14ZvmOiW7DVap&amp;itok=-giyJVrG" media="(max-width: 768px)" width="960" height="1224"/><source srcSet="https://www.groupe-sncf.com/medias-publics/styles/original/public/2024-09/groupe-sncf-international-desktop-fond-transparent-l.png.webp?VersionId=CDfiljk7JyS1AtgJRzFyrxtFAeQzIr_